AndroidApp_Steward
-------------------
This is my first personal Android App. Steward is a personal belongings management tool with following basic functionalities,

Grid view list: images of belonging of the logged in user, click the image to edit the information;
Camera: take pictures to new belonging to add to your list;
Edit: edit the information of an article, including title, price and description; or delete it from the list;

The information of the belongings is stored in the SQLite database;

This app is tested on Android 4.1.2
